## Node name
-sname ${NODE_NAME}

## Cookie
-setcookie ${ERLANG_COOKIE}

## QUIC distribution
-proto_dist quic
-epmd_module quic_epmd
-start_epmd false

## QUIC credentials (init args for quic_dist)
-quic_dist_cert ${QUIC_CERT_FILE}
-quic_dist_key ${QUIC_KEY_FILE}
-quic_dist_port ${QUIC_DIST_PORT}

## Increase distribution buffer size
+zdbbl 32768

## Enable kernel poll
+K true

## Async threads
+A 10
